snippet.title: Knights and Glory Official Preview Trailer
snippet.description:
Google Play: http://bit.ly/KnightsGlory (Open Beta)
App Store: https://apple.co/2znATPw

Knights and Glory is an online strategy card game with unique tactical battle simulation mechanics that focuses on conflicts between medieval civilizations around the world.

Official Page: http://playplayfun.com/knights-and-glory-game-official-page/
Facebook: https://fb.me/KnightsAndGlory
Twitter: https://twitter.com/glory_knights
